Class DiscreteTerm

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.ModelTerm

        • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.DiscreteTerm

  • @Embeddable
public final class DiscreteTerm
extends SingleVariableTerm

    A ModelTerm related to a particular option of a DiscreteVariable. Presents an immutable public interface.

    Per Effective Java Item 17, this class is marked final because it was not designed for inheritance.
